<br>
We don't need to find a mob that's as hard as VSR, we just need to find situations that require organization and people making intelligent decisions - like listening and following orders.<br>
<br>
We took down VS ( the one spawned from the Druid / Ranger turnins to VSR, not the REAL VS ) last night, and I was unable to land Cripple or Slow on him, even after a tash.  I suggest we get a high level Shammy for the real VS.  I was -real- worried about getting aggro with the mini-VS.  A caster getting aggro from the REAL VS will make a quick corpse, and possibly a raid wipe. <p>Zymyool, Officer of the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ancientadventurers.org"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Ancient Adventurers</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> on the Karana Server<br>
